# TechNexus MERN — environment template
# Copy the service-specific files below; never commit real secrets.
#
#   backend/.env   — API, MongoDB, JWT, Stripe, Gemini
#   frontend/.env  — React API URL, Stripe publishable key
#
# SECURITY: If a Gemini (or any) API key was ever exposed, revoke it in
# Google Cloud Console and create a new key before deploying.

# See backend/.env.example for full backend variables
# See frontend/.env.example for full frontend variables
